Retrieve all matching records in a single list.

```pycon
>>> table = api.table('base_id', 'table_name')
>>> table.all(view='MyView', fields=['ColA', '-ColB'])
[{'fields': ...}, ...]
>>> table.all(max_records=50)
[{'fields': ...}, ...]
```

